729806f-a.title: Richmond: Van Duzer Street - Sands Street
729806f-a.text:
Van Durer Street, west side, south from Sands
to Prospect Streets. In the right background appears the
steeple of the Evangelical Lutheran Church, on St. Pauls
Avenue.
May 25, 1935
P. L. Sperr
